# i18n

- Locales: `ko`, `ja`, `en`, `zh`, `my` (`src/i18n/config.ts`)
- Messages: `src/i18n/messages/{locale}.json` — add the **same key to all five** files
- Client: `const { t, locale, setLocale } = useTranslations()`
- Lookup: `t("nav.speakToday")` (dot paths)
- Persist locale via cookie/localStorage key `jlptcode-locale`
- Language UI: `LanguageSwitcher` in MainNavbar (select + flag), transparent styling per existing CSS
- When adding nav/home labels, update JSON keys and `NAV_LINKS` / home card constants together
